The paper addresses the problem of fairness and transparency in online marketplaces selling digital content, which involves security, distributed systems, data structures, software engineering, and cryptography. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
